content: Can you describe the project a bit more?

The AI then provided the user with two options regarding the shade of blue and whether to change the text color for better readability, along with a checklist of additional features they might want to implement, such as a customizable color palette, a toggle switch for light/dark mode, and social media sharing buttons. The user chose to add a button that triggers an alert in the browser, and the AI confirmed it would proceed with this addition. Following this, the AI presented additional options for the alert button, including the type of alert message and its placement on the site. Throughout the conversation, the user was actively engaged in selecting features and providing feedback on their preferences.
